    Located just east of Gresham, the Sandy River is a premier destination:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Best Spots</strong>: Dodge Park, Oxbow Regional Park, Cedar Creek Hatchery.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Tips</strong>: Use brightly colored jigs or bait to cut through murky post-rain water.
    </li>
</ul>
<h3>
    <strong>Clackamas River</strong>
</h3>
